'''''To Walk with Lions''''' ni film yo mu 1999 iyobowe na Carl Schultz ikinwamo na Richard Harris nka George Adamson na John Michie nka Tony Fitzjohn <ref>https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/to_walk_with_lions</ref>. Bikurikiranye imyaka yakurikiyeho Ntare wunganira Adamson<ref>https://www.tvguide.com/movies/to-walk-with-lions/cast/2030060527/</ref>. Nyuma yo gushyingiranwa na Joy Adamson wa ''Born Free'' fame, Adamson yamaze igice cya nyuma cyubuzima bwe arinda intare nâ€™ibindi binyabuzima muri Kora National Reserve, [[Kenya]] <ref>https://secondsightfilms.co.uk/products/to-walk-with-lions-dvd</ref>. Ahura na ba rushimusi na ruswa ya leta imubuza gushaka kubungabunga inyamaswa<ref>https://www.primevideo.com/detail/To-Walk-With-Lions/0K65C4TU3C4P9BOZW496707A4E</ref>.

== Umugambi ==
Tony Fitzjohn (John Michie) aje gukora kuri Kora, kubungabunga intare, kubavandimwe babiri bageze mu zabukuru, George na Terence Adamson ( Ian Bannen )<ref>https://wildlifenow.com/to-walk-with-lions-trailer/</ref>. Ku munsi we wa mbere, Fitzjohn yirengagije inama za George zo kutiruka kandi hafi yarakubiswe<ref>https://www.timeout.com/movies/to-walk-with-lions</ref>. Kumenyeshwa ubu nuburyo umuntu wa nyuma wujuje umwanya we yapfuye<ref>https://mubi.com/films/to-walk-with-lions</ref>, Fitzjohn yanditse ahantu hose nk'umusazi ahitamo kugenda<ref>https://www.bestbuy.com/site/to-walk-with-lions-dvd-1999/19303174.p?skuId=19303174</ref>. Nyuma yumunota wanyuma uhinduye umutima, hamwe n'icyana cy'intare cyamuzanye muri pariki kugirango amutoze kandi yongere yinjire mwishyamba, avumbura umuhamagaro wukuri mubuzima bwe<ref>https://bestsimilar.com/movies/24195-to-walk-with-lions</ref>.

